query:
WITH
       pfe AS (
              INSERT INTO profile_feed_entries (profile_feed_id, feed_entry_id)
              VALUES ($1, $2)
                  ON CONFLICT (profile_feed_id, feed_entry_id) DO
             NOTHING
           RETURNING id
       )
SELECT id AS "id!"
  FROM pfe
 UNION ALL
SELECT id
  FROM profile_feed_entries
 WHERE profile_feed_id = $1
   AND feed_entry_id = $2
